description.plain: Formed in 1988, Insane Poetry is one of the first and oldest horrorcore groups in hip hop history. The members vary but the founding member (CYCO) always remains. Their first LP ‘Grim Reality’ was released in 1992. Before and after that, they were part of Rodney O’s and Vanilla Ice’s crew – Tha Hit-Men and worked on the 1993 album; ‘Fuck New York’ and the 1994 album; ‘Mind Blowin’. Outside of their debut album, Insane Poetry’s two biggest albums are Faith in Chaos (2003) and The Snuff Reels (2008). They gained a more cult following through the Juggalo circuits after playing with Vanilla Ice at the Gathering.
